{
  "texts": [
    "The evidence is especially strong that private schooling is correlated with higher levels of political tolerance and political knowledge and skills.",
    "Religious private schooling is strongly associated with positive civic outcomes.",
    "Claims that private schooling imperils democracy are inconsistent with this empirical evidence.",
    "Our paper proceeds as follows.",
    "We first define civic values and draw from the psychology and political science literatures to describe the competing theories of supporters of public and private schools regarding their effects on civic outcomes."
  ]
}